results.name: Numbers k such that 9*k! + 1 is prime.
comment: Tested to 4500. - _Robert G. Wilson v_, Sep 28 2010
link: Index entries for sequences related to numbers of primes of the form k*n!+-1
mathematica: fQ[n_] := PrimeQ[9 n! + 1]; k = 0; lst = {}; While[k < 1501, If[ fQ@k, AppendTo[lst, k]; Print@k]; k++ ]; lst
